{
  "stem": "5970.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you were outdoors the whole day, from 5 o'clock in the morning till-- till the evening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all we were given was a portion of soup during the day and then in the evening a slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was just terribly, terribly cold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were-- we were-- we were carrying stones, that's all I remember, from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was no aim to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was no-- no purpose.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were just told to carry the stones from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we did get to see the camp around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I also forgot to mention that at the-- when we arrived in-- in Auschwitz, Mengele did the selection.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they used to call him the Angel of Death, the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he did the-- the choosing, the-- the pointing to the left and to the right.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This-- this-- we came in contact with a lot of strange people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were German prisoners there as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There were the Bibelforschers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They-- they had a different color of triangle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I think it was a lilac one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there were the-- the murderers and-- and real, you know, prisoners that they-- instead of keeping them in prisons, they sent them in-- into the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And one of them was our overseer, this kapo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was-- he-- he was in charge of these different groups of 10.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH], he was boasting how many people he killed before the war and while he was in there-- a real criminal.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But he wasn't too bad to us, because he was in-- in prison, I suppose, a long time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he was in charge of this group.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But what we did-- I really don't know what we did there.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
